OL,3,CCouple jailed in Iran on espionage
OL,4,Ccharges lose appeal, family says
OL,6,FA couple from Sussex jailed on spying
OL,7,Fcharges in Iran have lost an appeal
OL,8,Fagainst their convictions, their
OL,9,Ffamily has said.
OL,11,FCraig and Lindsay Foreman were handed
OL,12,Fa 10-year prison sentence in February
OL,13,Fafter being convicted of espionage,
OL,14,Fwhich they both deny.
OL,16,FThe pair's family have claimed they
OL,17,Fwere not permitted to attend their
OL,18,Fappeal hearing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
