OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780488668
OL,3,CCouple jailed in Iran on espionage
OL,4,Ccharges lose appeal, family says
OL,6,FThey were jailed following their
OL,7,Farrest in January 2025 while
OL,8,Ftravelling through Iran during an
OL,9,Faround-the-world trip by motorcycle.
OL,11,FMs Foreman's son Joe Bennett said "the
OL,12,Fdial needs to shift" as he explained
OL,13,Fthat the pair "don't understand the
OL,14,Fprocess".
OL,16,FHe said: "My mum Lindsay and step-dad
OL,17,FCraig were not permitted to attend
OL,18,Ftheir own appeal hearing.
OL,26,@sD@cOUtD@TO]uD@OOUvD@HO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780488668
OL,3,CCouple jailed in Iran on espionage
OL,4,Ccharges lose appeal, family says
OL,6,F"We don't know if they received a
OL,7,Fproper account of what was argued on
OL,8,Ftheir behalf.
OL,10,F"We know they had been asked to sign
OL,11,Fdocuments... documents they could not
OL,12,Fread, and they refused, but we don't
OL,13,Fknow the details of when, or what they
OL,14,Fwere.
OL,16,F"Their case has now passed to the
OL,17,FSupreme Court, but we don't understand
OL,18,Fthe process, the timeline, or what, if
OL,19,Fanything, will be submitted in their
OL,20,Fname."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
