PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780488668
OL,3,CCouple jailed in Iran on espionage
OL,4,Ccharges lose appeal, family says
OL,6,FThe pair's family said Mr Foreman is
OL,7,Fon day 25 of his hunger strike and Ms
OL,8,FForeman is on day 16 of hers, adding
OL,9,Fthat all communication between them
OL,10,Fhas been cut off by Iranian
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FMr Bennett said he met with officials
OL,14,Fat the Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,15,FDevelopment Office (FCDO) on Monday
OL,16,Fbut left without "clarity on what
OL,17,Fpressure is being applied to Tehran".
OL,19,FHe continued: "Their appeal has failed
OL,20,Fand they don't know why.
OL,26,@xD@ROUyD@dO]{D@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
