PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780488668
OL,3,CCouple jailed in Iran on espionage
OL,4,Ccharges lose appeal, family says
OL,6,F"They are on hunger strike because
OL,7,Fthey have run out of ways to make
OL,8,Ftheir own government act.
OL,10,F"The FCDO met with us yesterday and
OL,11,Fwere very kind. But kind is not the
OL,12,Fsame as doing something to enable
OL,13,Ftheir release.
OL,15,F"The dial needs to shift, and it needs
OL,16,Fto shift now."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
